Class AbstractBuilder<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • by.schepov.motordepot.builder.AbstractBuilder<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the element to be build by the builder
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Builder<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CarBuilder, CarNameBuilder, OrderBuilder, RequestBuilder, UserBuilder

    public abstract class AbstractBuilder<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Builder<T>
    Abstract class implementing Builder interface. Offers a default constructor AbstractBuilder() refreshing the object inside the builder and the simplest implementation of build() method. Contains a protected field object representing the object being constructed.
